<i>noun</i>: 광우병 <br>
<ul>
<li>
<i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>광우병</dt><br>
<dd>a fatal disease of cattle that affects the central nervous system; causes staggering and agitation</dd><br>
<dd><i>synonyms</i>: bovine spongiform encephalitis, BSE, mad cow disease</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>
